flowchart TD
    A[data/songs.csv] --> B[load_songs]
    B --> C[songs list]

    U[user_prefs dictionary] --> D[recommend_songs]
    C --> D

    D --> E[Pick one song from songs list]
    E --> F[Compare song fields to user profile targets]
    F --> G[Compute compatibility score]
    G --> H[Attach explanation]
    H --> I[Store tuple: song, score, explanation]

    I --> J{More songs left?}
    J -->|Yes| E
    J -->|No| K[Sort all tuples by score descending]

    K --> L[Take top-k]
    L --> M[Ranked recommendations printed in main.py]
